    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the goblin thing is just... weird. it doesnt change anything. the reality is i've tried everything. i've tried therapy, i've tried different habits, i've tried changing my life. but the loop is too strong. it feels like the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just break the machine entirely. the loop only ends one way.",
